<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>SARAM THISEN IN A SI LO CH134</title>
<key>C</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Judah Biak theng cungah, Saram phunphun an thah; Siseh cu saram thisen
 nih, Sualnak a tawl kho lo.

[V2]
 Siseh Pathian Tuufa, Kan sualnak kalpitu, A thi in sualtlanh thawinak
 cu, Saram nakin sung deuh.

[V3]
 Keimah nih ka zumh i, Na khamhnak ka hmuh cang, Sualnak vialte kaa
 ngaihchih i, Na sin ka phuan Bawipa.

[V4]
 Vailamtahnak cungah, Sifahnak kha na in, Ka lung in ka ruah tikah cun,
 Na kan dawtnak ka hngalh.

[V5]
 Biaknak Pathian Tuufa, A zummi lunglawmhnak, Ka zumh i biak ka duh ko
 cang, A dawtnak ka thangthat.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>134</hymn_number>
</song>